/*
  Grants a +1 enhancement bonus to all weapons  equipped
  by a target of the spell. Lasts 1 turn per level.
*/
//:://////////////////////////////////////////////
//:: Created By: Andrew Nobbs
//:: Created On: Nov 28, 2002
